-- EFG-Hermes Builds $1.2 Billion North African Investment Fund, Al Alam Says
-- Ola Galal
-- 2010-06-13T06:32:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/egypt-s-efg-hermes-building-1-billion-euro-investment-fund-al-alam-says.html

          
          
             EFG-Hermes Holding SAE aims to
collect 1 billion euros ($1.2 billion) in a fund for investments
in countries including Morocco and Egypt,  Al Alam Al Youm 
reported, citing  Hazem Shawki , a bank official.  
 The investment bank has already collected 400 million euros
and also plans to set up another fund valued at 1 billion
Egyptian pounds ($176.2 million), the Cairo-based newspaper
said.  
